  "readme_html": "\n        \n          <p><img src=\"https://github.com/jmorganca/ollama/assets/251292/8dab1157-909a-455b-a5c4-f7c31e9bcf0e\" width=\"400\"/></p>\n\n<p>Zephyr is a series of language models that are trained to act as helpful assistants. Zephyr 141B-A35B is the latest model in the series, and is a fine-tuned version of <a href=\"https://ollama.com/library/mixtral:8x22b\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mixtral 8x22b</a>.</p>\n\n<h2>Sizes</h2>\n\n<ul>\n<li><code>zephyr:141b</code>: A Mixture of Experts (MoE) model with 141B total parameters and 35B active parameters.</li>\n<li><code>zephyr:7b</code>: The original Zephyr model</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Source:</h2>\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/HuggingFaceH4\" rel=\"nofollow\">HuggingFace</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n        \n      ",
